data.description: Welcome to this charming top floor home featuring extraordinary vaulted ceilings & wonderful natural light. Walk up to the top corner unit. Plenty of storage for pantry and large closets. Kitchen features updated light fixture, big window and dishwasher. The main living area has a real wood burning fire place, space for a dining room table, and full living room set up. The porch gets plenty of south facing sun and is a great place to sip your morning coffee or wind down with glass of wine. The bedroom has soaring ceilings, a massive closet with custom sliding barn door. My favorite feature is the cute little tucked away loft that the Seller used as an office. The bathroom has been updated and there is a laundry room for in unit laundry! Pets allowed. Enjoy the community pool this summer. Ample off street parking for you and guests. Walking distance to Dry Dock Brewery. Close to amenities, grocery shopping,  Aurora Golf course, 12 miles stables, and amazing open space walking trails with access all the way to Cherry Creek Reservoir! Easy access to airport and downtown. If you are looking for a clean, bright, easy lock and leave, look no further!
